query:
SELECT u.id as user_id, u.name, u.email, u.role, tp.id as tutor_profile_id, tp.approvalStatus 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN tutor_profiles tp ON u.id = tp.userId 
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Maya%' OR u.name LIKE '%Shriti%' OR u.email LIKE '%maya%' OR u.email LIKE '%shriti%';
